'''电感耦合等离子体原子发射光谱法'''（Inductively coupled plasma atomic emission spectroscopy，缩写ICP-AES），也称为电感耦合等离子体光学发射光谱法（inductively coupled plasma optical emission spectrometry，缩写ICP-OES），是利用通过高频电感耦合产生等离子体放电的光源来进行[[原子发射光谱法|原子发射光谱]]分析的方法。它是一种火焰温度范围为6000至10000K的火焰技术。该发射强度表示样品中元素的浓度。为一种新型激发光源，性能优异，应用广泛。

== 组成 ==
[[File:ICP-AES_Plasma_Torch_-_001.jpg|thumb]]
主要包括等离子体炬管、高频发生器（产生高频电流）、感应圈、供气系统和雾化系统。炬管由三层同心[[石英|石英]]玻璃管组成<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Hieftje|first1=Gary|display-authors=etal|title=Design and Construction of a Low-Flow, Low-Power Torch for Inductively Coupled Plasma Spectrometry|journal=Applied Spectroscopy|date=1982|volume=36|issue=6|pages=627–631|url=http://www.opticsinfobase.org/as/abstract.cfm?uri=as-36-6-627|accessdate=5 April 2015|bibcode=1982ApSpe..36..627R|doi=10.1366/0003702824639105|archive-date=2015-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150424161746/http://www.opticsinfobase.org/as/abstract.cfm?uri=as-36-6-627|dead-url=no}}</ref>。外管内切向通入的[[氩气|氩气]]为等离子体工作气或冷却气。中管通入的氩气为辅助气。内管中的氩气为载气，将试样[[气溶胶|气溶胶]]引入炬中。

== 应用 ==
ICP-AES的应用实例包括测定[[葡萄酒|葡萄酒]]中的金属<ref name="pmid11820494">{{cite journal |vauthors=Aceto M, Abollino O, Bruzzoniti MC, Mentasti E, Sarzanini C, Malandrino M | title = Determination of metals in wine with atomic spectroscopy (flame-AAS, GF-AAS and ICP-AES); a review | journal = Food additives and contaminants | volume = 19 | issue = 2 | pages = 126–33 | date = 2002 | pmid = 11820494 | doi =10.1080/02652030110071336 }}</ref>，食物中的[[砷|砷]]<ref name="pmid10497786">{{cite journal |vauthors=Benramdane L, Bressolle F, Vallon JJ | title = Arsenic speciation in humans and food products: a review | journal = Journal of chromatographic science | volume = 37 | issue = 9 | pages = 330–44 | date = 1999 | pmid = 10497786 | doi = 10.1093/chromsci/37.9.330}}</ref>，以及与[[蛋白质|蛋白质]]结合的微量元素<ref name="pmid15300764">{{cite journal |vauthors=Ma R, McLeod CW, Tomlinson K, Poole RK | title = Speciation of protein-bound trace elements by gel electrophoresis and atomic spectrometry | journal = Electrophoresis | volume = 25 | issue = 15 | pages = 2469–77 | date = 2004 | pmid = 15300764 | doi = 10.1002/elps.200405999}}</ref>。

ICP-OES广泛应用于[[选矿工程|选矿工程]]过程，以提供各种物流等级的数据，用于质量平衡的构建。

